addons.text:
We value the time-honored traditions of Christian service, education, and unconditional love to benefit all of God’s creation. We will serve our community as an educational and informational resource center. We will give back to our community through professional guidance and personal and specialized attention civic service organizations, and a local church. overlay_none 0 0 0 0 #ffffff #addonId .sppb-addon-text-block {
   letter-spacing: -0.33px;
}

In everything we do, we strive to meet and exceed the expectations of the families we serve. We will be known in our community for our commitment to excellence in community service. overlay_none 0 0 0 0 #ffffff #addonId .sppb-addon-text-block {
   letter-spacing: -0.33px;
}

Our sole purpose is a holistic approach to develop community-based educational and artistic programs, designed to mold individuals into morally responsible citizens in body, mind, and spirit. This will serve as a bridge between home, school, church, and the community. It is more than just bringing together people, but to remediate low academic skills, to build self-esteem and to serve as an alternative to prevent drugs, violence, and crime. Its main function is to provide a wide variety of well-planned and professionally directed activities for those who themselves are in a period of physical and social transition, and thus need close personal warmth and understanding. overlay_none 0 0 0 0 #ffffff #addonId .sppb-addon-text-block {
   letter-spacing: -0.33px;
}

Such experience will include the acquiring of basic knowledge and understandings, improving the self-esteem concept, developing proper study habits, promoting interpersonal human relations, physical development through recreational activities and inter-cultural understanding and appreciation. overlay_none 0 0 0 0 #ffffff #addonId .sppb-addon-text-block {
   letter-spacing: -0.33px;
}

